<div class = "app-card-container">
    <div class = "card">    
        <h1 class="text-center">About Me</h1>

        <hr>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <%= image_tag "merry-xmas.jpg", width:250, alt:"profile_image" %>
            
                <div class="skills">
                    <% @skills.each do|skill|%>
                    <h5><%= skill.title %></h5>
                        <div class="progress">
                            <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated"
                            role="progressbar" 
                            aria-valuenow="<%=skill.percent_utilized%>" 
                            aria-valuemax="100"
                            style="width:<%=skill.percent_utilized%>%">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-8">
                <p>
                I started my education in mechanical engineering but my interests diverged into software development so I began my education into full stack outside of the university. With many resources being open source, I believe the development community has a personality that is key to reviving the educational system.
                </p>

                <p>
                    <button 
                        class="btn btn-warning"
                        type="button"
                        data-toggle="collapse"
                        data-target="#jobHistory"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controller="jobHistory"
                    >
                        Job History
                    </button>

                    <button 
                        class="btn btn-warning"
                        type="button"
                        data-toggle="collapse"
                        data-target="#education"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controller="education"
                    >
                        Education
                    </button>
                </p>

                <p>
                    <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Job 1
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Job 2
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>

                <p>
                    <div class="collapse" id="education">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            School 1
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            School 2
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>